 :notes
 ["This solution catalog entry maps to the 014-key-delegation-passports coding guide and its daemon-side implementation."
  "Statuses reflect the single-hop MVP path; multi-hop delegation chains remain explicitly guarded at `max_chain_depth > 0`."
  "The inline-verifier design keeps proxy-signed artifacts self-contained: consumers verify from the embedded proof without fetching the full delegation passport."
